body:
UVM tests/50cmdlineproc/50UVM_TIMEOUT/01mainphase and a few others fail because time incorrectly advances after a $finish executes.

```
module t;
  task phase();
    #1000;
  endtask
  initial begin
    fork
      phase();
    join_none
    #123;
    $finish;
  end
  final begin
    $display("[%0t] final (should be 123)", $time);
    if ($time != 123) $stop;
  end
endmodule
```

